Launch Terminal: Meta+Return
Launch Browser: Meta+Ctrl+Return
Launch Program: Meta+Space
Quick Actions: Meta+y

${chalk.blue("## Window management")}
You can click and drag a window's titlebar to move it around.
To close a window, either press Meta+Shift+q, or middle-click
the window's title bar.

To put a window into float mode, press Meta+Shift+f.

To resize windows, press Meta+r, which will out you in "resize
mode"--then use the arrow keys to change dimensions, and hit
Return when you are done.

To switch between horizontal/vertical layout, press Meta+e. For
tabbed layout, press Meta+w. To turn the current window into a
tabbed container, press Meta+Shift+w.

${chalk.blue("## Settings")}
Having audio troubles and need a GUI? Run \`pavucontrol\` in a
terminal. For managing bluetooth devices, run \`blueman-manager\`.

${chalk.blue("## Etc")}
To take a screenshot, press the "Print Screen" key. Screenshots
are saved in \`~/Pictures/screenshots\`.

To lock the screen, press Meta+Escape.

For everything else, refer to config files found in
\`~/.local/share/chezmoi\`.

This machine is running Ubuntu, the i3 window manager, and
alacritty+zsh. The compositor is picom, and the statusbar at the
bottom is polybar. Dotfiles are managed using chezmoi.

Enjoy! ðŸš€
